{"tid":1477199,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"be water 香港各區地利形勢和地形的考慮","createTime":"2019-08-16T05:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T06:25:42.000Z","uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9197fb0956e670e200d4c1bfee1c061b3fe2f88","tid":1477199,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"怕重現811, 唔想有手足出事<br />\n大家本來想be water, hit and run<br />\n但811, 大家不知道去那, 結果有鬼就像牧羊犬那樣, 帶領羊群<br />\n太古, 明顯是個不利地形和環境, 加上早已埋伏既黑警, 結果手足比黑警近距離瘋狂掃射, 想走也走不到<br />\n地形, 地理, 建築物, 屏障是很重要的, 就算be water, 都要揀有利的環境, 而且要避免比黑警事前伏兵<br />\n<br />\n例如深水埗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmxjUuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmxjUuH.png&h=2baab402&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5個黨鐵站, 就算黨鐵想封站, 都要圍晒5個. 而家黨鐵聽命中共, 黨鐵其實不是安全地方, 記住這點<br />\n深水埗極多小巷, 街道極散, 四通八達, 黑警想全方位推進和封鎖, 都不是易事<br />\n簡單講, 深水步可以全方位散水, 5個黨鐵站, 一堆巴士站, 一堆建築物, 一堆商鋪, 一堆居民<br />\n<br />\n例如天水圍狗屋個地勢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x1wpk92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx1wpk92.png&h=e977c299&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n背面(西面)係屋邨, 屋邨後面有條河, <br />\n河前面有圍欄, 你想跳河走都跳唔到<br />\n狗屋後路(西面)冇得走, 狗可以封少一面<br />\n得番對出條大路<br />\n北面係屋苑商場 理論上可以走<br />\n但狗一封天湖路個路口 又封死一面<br />\n最後再係地鐵站同天福路放啲狗 <br />\n你地根本冇可能有得走"},{"pid":"dacf8a34c9377741b570b5a7db34e91bc1d9a143","tid":1477199,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahzZa5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahzZa5a.png&h=7faf7d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角個形勢好似唔錯<br />\n四通八達<br />\n無私人地方 多建築 可以去太子/奧運/石硤尾/旺角/油麻地 黨鐵封唔晒d路<br />\n大量建築物 大量遊人<br />\n要全方位封鎖，黑警需要大量人手"},{"pid":"8c2385eb1aaac29a31a93bfb7ff788510b89dba7","tid":1477199,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dacf8a34c9377741b570b5a7db34e91bc1d9a143","tid":1477199,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahzZa5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahzZa5a.png&h=7faf7d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角個形勢好似唔錯<br />\n四通八達<br />\n無私人地方 多建築 可以去太子/奧運/石硤尾/旺角/油麻地 黨鐵封唔晒d路<br />\n大量建築物 大量遊人<br />\n要全方位封鎖，黑警需要大量人手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:12:03.000Z","msg":"最弊鑊鑊喺彌敦道等死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1e6525b2cdd4b25f171960a57fa82918d1f8bd","tid":1477199,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SkJSv7V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkJSv7V.png&h=8335714c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太古根本個地形好差<br />\n近山果面 私人地方 再上就是山<br />\n一邊向海<br />\n仲有無大量小路走，唔係四通八達<br />\n黨鐵實停你站<br />\n一封條路 基本無得走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24aa481ef9df432318a741c20d889738c77e96fc","tid":1477199,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"咁禮賓府如何？<br />\n就咁好似易上難落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQSv2gm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQSv2gm.png&h=4e1be38e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b855e175d5f25e80d4a18951d9d814ade79afbb","tid":1477199,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁禮賓府如何？<br />\n就咁<span style=\"color: red;\">睇</span>好似<span style=\"color: red;\">易落難上</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQSv2gm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQSv2gm.png&h=4e1be38e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e3aa690d62823030a5573a776b00904533764189","tid"